1
00:05:23,709 --> 00:05:26,875
It’s beyond Me to really express

2
00:05:28,999 --> 00:05:32,667
the great joy

3
00:05:34,834 --> 00:05:40,875
that I see in your hearts,

4
00:05:41,917 --> 00:05:44,709
reflected in My heart.

5
00:05:46,208 --> 00:05:49,250
Today’s a great day I think,

6
00:05:50,166 --> 00:05:54,208
that we have come to a place

7
00:05:54,417 --> 00:05:57,999
which is in Italy

8
00:05:58,542 --> 00:06:02,375
and the Austrians are going to do the Guru Puja.

9
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:10,375
Because it’s such an integration of understanding.

10
00:06:20,208 --> 00:06:26,083
It’s a very new beginning of a new world,

11
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:30,792
the vision of which I had since long,

12
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:35,834
because this world is one, created by one God.

13
00:06:36,125 --> 00:06:41,375
All these demarcations are man-made

14
00:06:41,625 --> 00:06:44,667
and they create problems.

15
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:51,375
In Sahaja Yoga you realize that we are all one

16
00:06:51,875 --> 00:06:56,417
part and parcel of one great Virata.

17
00:06:59,625 --> 00:07:02,000
This has to be understood,

18
00:07:03,041 --> 00:07:04,834
that

19
00:07:07,166 --> 00:07:10,750
this joy comes out of the love

20
00:07:10,999 --> 00:07:14,875
and affection we have for each other

21
00:07:15,041 --> 00:07:19,999
and for our Mother and the Creator.

22
00:07:23,834 --> 00:07:26,875
So open your heart

23
00:07:27,083 --> 00:07:29,959
open your heart.

24
00:07:32,792 --> 00:07:39,750
And everything will be enjoyable, beautiful,

25
00:07:40,208 --> 00:07:42,667
and you will feel

26
00:07:44,709 --> 00:07:48,792
the ambrosia trickling into your being,

27
00:07:48,999 --> 00:07:53,417
into your nerves all around you.

28
00:07:54,875 --> 00:07:58,583
The joy can be only complete

29
00:07:58,834 --> 00:08:00,750
when you can receive it

30
00:08:00,959 --> 00:08:03,999
every minute, every moment.

31
00:08:05,583 --> 00:08:09,542
And that is what I want all of you to have.

32
00:08:09,792 --> 00:08:12,125
That’s My pure desire.

33
00:08:12,333 --> 00:08:15,667
May God bless you all.

